#

Easy Pork Quesadillas

20 min
$12
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Quick MealCheesySavory

Description

Crispy tortillas filled with savory pulled pork and melted cheese, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • flour tortillas: 4 large
  • cooked pulled pork: 2 cups
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or monterey jack): 2 cups
  • sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • salsa: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • chopped green onions: 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
